                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6057" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1530</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8307 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小稻米，大故事：赵钱孙李公司的大米产业一体化发展之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A case study of the integrated development strategy of Zhao Qian Sun Li Rice Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曲秉春，黄百卉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东北师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">盘锦赵钱孙李实业有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大米；纵向一体化；多元化；赵钱孙李公司；农业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Rice; Vertical integration; Diversification; Zhao Qian Sun Li Company; Agricultural</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了在盘锦赵钱孙李公司以冷鲜储运，粥米、蒸饭米、炒饭米组合的产品创新战略迅速切入盘锦高端大米市场后，以赵钱孙李大米品牌为龙头，沿着稻米产业链进行了前后一体化的大米产业生态建设。在前向一体化方向上，为构建与消费者一体化的关系，建设大米博物馆和盘锦农特产博物园，形成了特色的体验式产品销售终端，融入了盘锦文旅的大生态中，形成产品销售的流量担当，开创了农业与文旅产业的高度融合模式。在后向一体化方向上，经过锲而不舍的探寻和试验，掌握了大米种植田间管理的核心工艺，并发现了独特的酱香稻米品种，田间管理工艺与酱香品种相互配合，创造了盘锦大米历史上的新高度；在产品线的建设上，打造了稻米油、清酒大吟酿、味淋的产品组合，形成了一体化的大米产业链。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study describes the before- and after- chain relation of rice industry ecological construction in Panjin Zhao Qian Sun Li Rice company, which, taking Zhao-Qian-Sun-Li Rice Brand as the leader, has quickly entered the Panjin high-end rice market, using the product innovation strategy by integrating into one cold storage transportation, porridge rice, steamed rice, fried rice. 

The before-chain relation was to set up a tie with consumers. Two museums were established: Rice Museum and Panjin Agricultural Specialties Museum, forming a characteristic experiential product sales terminal. The product was integrated into the Panjin culture and tourism ecology, making a steady flow of product sales and a high degree of integration model of agriculture and tourism industry. 



For the after-chain relation, persistent exploration and experiment were carried out, so that principle techniques of rice planting and field management were obtained and a unique Maotai-fragrant rice variety was found, reaching a new height in Panjin rice history. The company also exploited the new production line, with rice oil, sake wine and flavor rice integrated as another rice industry chain.

</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略制定、战略选择、纵向一体化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
